{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KfiSjJJp5Kxq9xyVE1k7dX","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-28\n     2→\n     3→### Session 71 — state corruption fix #55, no-op (2026-03-28T10:22Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **State corruption fix #55**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, done count dropped from 74 to 70.\n     6→- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.\n     7→- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done` in both sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml, updated sprint totals (70->74).\n     8→- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 55th occurrence.\n     9→- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n    10→- **CRITICAL**: Ralph must be stopped. 55 consecutive no-op sessions wasting tokens on the same fix.\n    11→\n    12→## Token Report\n    13→- Total tool calls: ~12\n    14→- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 4, Edit: 6, Grep: 0, Write: 0, Glob: 4\n    15→- Files read: 3 unique, 4 total reads\n    16→- Redundant operations: None — known recurring issue efficiently fixed\n    17→\n    18→### Session 70 — state corruption fix #54, no-op (2026-03-28T10:20Z)\n    19→\n    20→- **State corruption fix #54**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, done count dropped from 74 to 70.\n    21→- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.\n    22→- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done` in both sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml, updated sprint totals (70->74).\n    23→- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 54th occurrence.\n    24→- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n    25→- **CRITICAL**: Ralph must